title: Windows XP Professional SP3 x86 - Integrated March 2014
description:
Windows XP Professional SP3 x86 Integrated March 2014

This is the original Microsoft Windows XP Professional SP3 (32-bit) ISO (Volume License) including Microsoft updates until 11.03.2014, Internet Explorer 8, Adobe Flash Player (12.0.0.77), Chipset and SATA drivers.


This version is the best from the internet and contains:

- NO tweaks or add-ons.
- NO additional programs and software added.
- NO graphics, scripts and wallpapers added or changed.
- Windows Messenger, MSN Explorer and Internet Explorer 6 were removed.
- It's the original image from Microsoft except added updates, IE8, Adobe Flash Player, Chipset and SATA drivers.

System requirements:

- Pentium 233-megahertz (MHz) processor or faster (300 MHz is recommended).
- At least 64 megabytes (MB) of RAM (128 MB is recommended).
- At least 1.5 gigabytes (GB) of available space on the hard disk .
- Video adapter and monitor with Super VGA (800 x 600) or higher resolution
